-----------------To ENABLE running scripts
set-executionpolicy remotesigned

-----------------To DISABLE running scripts
set-executionpolicy restricted

-----------------Then Import the modules from the scripts
Navigate to the ps1 files

-----------------Example
cd desktop

> Import-Module .\a.ps1
> Import-Module .\b.ps1
> Import-Module .\c.ps1
> a
> b
> c

_SC_ ==> indicates Windows Services on the machine
